race.comment: BLUE LAKODA (8) was in the placings last time but prior to that posted a swift 16.59 win over 300m at this track. Hot win two back and looks the one to beat here. PITTSWORTH FLYER (7) produced a moderate effort last time when fifth at Q Lakeside over 352m behind Federal Joker (20.30) in a Grade 6. Has ability and can measure up. BIRDS THE WORD (1) has mixed form recently, finishing seventh (20.00) in a Grade 6 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Can improve sharply here. VINDALOO (3) returns from a four-and-a-half months layoff and must be included.
